OL,3,C'Violent' and 'controlling' man
OL,4,Csentenced after months of abuse
OL,6,FA North Lincolnshire man who subjected
OL,7,Fa woman to months of torment has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,F27-year-old, Harley Wardell raped a
OL,11,Fwoman and later tried to run away from
OL,12,Fpolice when they were called to a
OL,13,Fproperty in Scunthorpe.
OL,15,FAt around 9am on Tuesday 23 July 2024,
OL,16,Fofficers arrived at an address on
OL,17,FWesley Street after reports of
OL,18,Fscreaming and shouting. They spoke to
OL,19,Fa visibly distressed woman in an
OL,20,Fupstairs window.
