OL,6,FAs they tried to gain entry, a man was
OL,7,Fseen trying to flee the property but
OL,8,Fwas caught following a brief chase.
OL,10,FHe was later identified as Wardell.
OL,12,FIt was found that during the morning,
OL,13,FWardell had become extremely violent
OL,14,Ftowards the woman, attempting to
OL,15,Fstrangle her and restrict her
OL,16,Fbreathing.
OL,18,FThe woman told officers that Wardell
OL,19,Fhad subjected her to repeated
OL,20,Fphysical, sexual, and emotional abuse
OL,21,Fover several months.
