OL,4,Csentenced after months of abuse
OL,6,FHumberside Police said she described
OL,7,Fbeing threatened with weapons,
OL,8,Fpunched, kicked, and prevented from
OL,9,Fleaving the property on numerous
OL,10,Foccasions.
OL,12,FWardell pleaded guilty to rape and
OL,13,Fintentional strangulation on Friday 12
OL,14,FSeptember 2025.
