OL,3,C'Violent' and 'controlling' man
OL,4,Csentenced after months of abuse
OL,6,FInsp Jayne Coutts said: "Wardell is a
OL,7,Fviolent and controlling man whose
OL,8,Factions are deeply disturbing, and
OL,9,Falthough they cannot be undone, I hope
OL,10,Fthis result provides some measure of
OL,11,Frelief that he has been held
OL,12,Faccountable.
OL,14,F"The courage showed by the woman in
OL,15,Fspeaking out about her experience has
OL,16,Fbeen remarkable, and I sincerely
OL,17,Fcommend her for her strength through
OL,18,Fthis understandably very difficult
OL,19,Fprocess."
